comments: Durant (BKN) brushes Barrett's (NYK) right arm and marginal contact occurs after Barrett's gather. After this initial contact, Drummond (BKN) is turning away from Barrett and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Sims (NYK) and Johnson (BKN) come together at the same spot off-ball and quickly disengage.

Sims (NYK) attempts to jump vertically contesting the driving shot attempt by Johnson (BKN) and absorbs a majority of the contact.  There is slight forward movement by Sims, but the body contact is deemed marginal.
Randle (NYK) jumps forward as he pursues the rebound and marginal body contact occurs with Drummond (BKN) as he elevates.
Sims (NYK) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away prior to incidental contact occurring with Johnson (BKN) or Drummond (BKN).
Johnson (BKN) initiates contact with Randle's (NYK) back and right arm after he retrieves the rebound.
Dragic (BKN) and Randle (NYK) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Dragic (BKN) is retreating alongside Randle's (NYK) path and absorbs the marginal body contact before cleanly dislodging the ball away during the drive.
Barrett (NYK) brings his right arm toward Durant's (BKN) path and marginal contact occurs to Durant's front during the drive.
Durant (BKN) brings his off-arm toward Barrett's (NYK) front and marginal contact occurs as Durant slows his momentum to release away.
Dragic (BKN) wraps Burks' (NYK) upper half with both arms and affects Burks' FOM as he moves to set the pick.
Johnson (BKN) brushes Randle's (NYK) left arm and Randle is able to move through the marginal contact to finish at the rim.
Barrett (NYK) and Durant (BKN) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Barrett (NYK) brings his right hand toward Durant's (BKN) left leg and marginal contact occurs as Durant elevates for the jump shot attempt.
Sims (NYK) and Claxton (BKN) engage and disengage with one another as they each attempt to establish rebounding position.
Burks (NYK) extends his arm in pursuit of the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Claxton's (BKN) left arm as they each attempt to retrieve the ball.
Dragic (BKN) moves alongside Randle (NYK) and maintains a legal guarding position after Randle picks up his dribble.
Claxton (BKN) briefly has his arms around Robinson's (NYK) midsection before correcting.
Fournier (NYK) engages and disengages with Brown (BKN) as he plants to cut during the inbound.
Brown (BKN) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away as Fournier (NYK) releases the pass.
Burks (NYK) commits a take foul on Durant (BKN).
Burks (NYK) and Durant (BKN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Burks (NYK) commits a take foul on Brown (BKN).
Johnson (BKN) commits a take foul on Barrett (NYK).
Robinson (NYK) and Barrett (NYK) engage and disengage with Durant (BKN) during the inbound.
Robinson (NYK) commits a take foul on Durant (BKN).
Claxton (BKN) brings his hand toward Randle's (NYK) back and marginal contact occurs as Randle mishandles the pass.
